TITLE: Implementing API Loader for Articles
DESCRIPTION: Creating a Remix loader function that fetches articles from the API and handles errors appropriately for use in the feed page.
SOURCE: https://github.com/feature-sliced/documentation/blob/master/i18n/en/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/get-started/tutorial.md#2025-04-19_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { json } from "@remix-run/node";

import { GET } from "shared/api";

export const loader = async () => {
  const { data: articles, error, response } = await GET("/articles");

  if (error !== undefined) {
    throw json(error, { status: response.status });
  }

  return json({ articles });
};
```

